I want to get to this collage in France called Gobelins and I’ve wanted to for 3 years now. It’s become a lot easier to justify my life when I have a goal, whatever works for you works, but just keep trying :)

The point is that everything is fleeting and to the universe it’s meaningless... if you want to do something about your situation, fight for it. If that’s not working, then hone in on some different skill. There’s not aime solution, in fact for many people there’s no solutions in general... but the point is to keep fighting for a better life, a better future.
